<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-21-0373 </DOCNO><TEXT>Advantages of alternative energy sources for agriculture are discussed.The author feels that at the present level of technology, solar energy,wind energy, and biogas are particularly suited as energy sources foragriculture. The technology and specific uses are described for thesethree energy sources. Expanding the use of draft animals is also urged,when feasible, for energy conservation.</TEXT></DOC>